text: The 2012 NCAA Division I Outdoor Track and Field Championships were the 91st NCAA Men's Division I Outdoor Track and Field Championships and the 31st NCAA Women's Division I Outdoor Track and Field Championships at Drake Stadium in Des Moines, Iowa on the campus of the Drake University from June 5–8, 2012.
